## 9. Build and Compilation

### 9.1 CMake Configuration

```cmake
cmake_minimum_required(VERSION 3.16)
project(HybridEncryptorServer)

set(CMAKE_CXX_STANDARD 17)           # C++17 features
find_package(OpenSSL REQUIRED)       # Find OpenSSL library

add_executable(hybrid_server
    main.cpp
    HybridEncryptor.cpp
    HybridDecryptor.cpp
    applink.c                         # Windows OpenSSL support
)

target_include_directories(hybrid_server PRIVATE
    ${OPENSSL_INCLUDE_DIR}
)

target_link_libraries(hybrid_server
    OpenSSL::Crypto                   # Cryptographic operations
    OpenSSL::SSL                      # SSL/TLS (if needed)
    ws2_32                            # Windows Sockets (Windows only)
    mswsock                           # Windows socket extensions
)
```

### 9.2 Build Commands

**Windows (Visual Studio):**
```bash
mkdir build
cd build
cmake .. -G "Visual Studio 16 2019" -A x64
cmake --build . --config Release
```

**Linux/Mac:**
```bash
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
cmake --build . --config Release
make
```

### 9.3 Dependencies

**Required Libraries:**
- OpenSSL 1.1.1 or later
  - libssl (SSL/TLS)
  - libcrypto (Cryptographic functions)
- C++ Standard Library (C++17)

**Included Headers:**
- Crow Web Framework (crow_all.h) - single header library
- Standard C++ headers (iostream, fstream, vector, etc.)

