## Appendix B: Glossary

| Term | Definition |
|------|-----------|
| **AES** | Advanced Encryption Standard (symmetric cipher) |
| **RSA** | Rivest-Shamir-Adleman (asymmetric cipher) |
| **Cipher** | Algorithm for encryption/decryption |
| **Plaintext** | Unencrypted original data |
| **Ciphertext** | Encrypted data |
| **Key** | Secret value used by cipher |
| **IV (Initialization Vector)** | Random value for CBC mode |
| **Padding** | Extra bytes added to align data to block size |
| **EVP** | Envelope API (high-level OpenSSL interface) |
| **OAEP** | Optimal Asymmetric Encryption Padding |
| **CBC** | Cipher Block Chaining mode |
| **PEM** | Privacy Enhanced Mail (key file format) |
| **JSON** | JavaScript Object Notation (data format) |
| **Base64** | Encoding scheme for binary data in text |
| **CORS** | Cross-Origin Resource Sharing |

